# Project Foundation: Diano Careers MVP 2.0

## Goal Description
Establish the architectural foundation for Diano Careers MVP 2.0. The setup focuses on a hybrid B2C/B2B structure, mobile-friendliness, scalability, and a calm, mentor-like UI utilizing Next.js, shadcn/ui, Tailwind CSS, Supabase, and Recharts.

## User Review Required
